---
title: Vietnamese-Style Mushroom & Chicken Rice Bowl with Cucumber Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: We love a classic Vietnamese-style rice bowl, so let’s put it to the test. There’s a collection of veggies including meaty mushrooms, tender chicken, a sticky plum sauce, plant-based mayo to mellow it out and a garnish of crispy shallots for crunch. It passes with flying colours!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
